1775  C4A8              ; DRAW SPRITE — IX=data, B=screen_x, C=screen_y
1776  C4A8              ; Fix 29: masked draw. For each byte: (screen AND ~pixel) OR pixel.
1777  C4A8              ; Sprite 0-pixels = transparent (background shows through).
1778  C4A8              ; Sprite 1-pixels = always drawn (foreground).
